Spader is fantastic!!!I love this show,absolutely brilliant.Excellent show that is very well written and acted,amazing story!!Spader plays an interesting character and his dialogue and delivery are fun to watch.The story line and the lead players are well chosen.The cast really blends well together.It is so refreshing to have a series that has real depth to it!The Blacklist is must see show in my opinion.It hooked me up since the very first episode.Every episode is full of suspense & wonder,i love that! Look forward and waiting 4 season!!Ones again must say James Spader is brilliant choice ,best acting I've ever seen and i watch allot of shows,i have never been hooked so quickly.Love James Spader!!!!